name: CryptoMite #1
description: This was the first captured CryptoMite. I hypothesize there to be roughly 100 out there, though there could be more.   I could only describe my feelings as astonishment and awe when I first discovered these entities.   This one had friendly and docile energy when first approached. Containment wasn't too difficult. I simply isolated its digital pattern and codified it into a comprehensible form.
